Package to.us.resume_builder.business.server_connect.request.impl

Class PDFRequest

java.lang.Object
to.us.resume_builder.business.server_connect.request.BasicRequest<java.io.InputStream>
to.us.resume_builder.business.server_connect.request.impl.PDFRequest
public class PDFRequest
extends BasicRequest<java.io.InputStream>
Request for PDF compilation to the Spring server; must be loaded with the LaTeX string to compile (as argument "latex"), and a boolean indicating whether the resultant PDF should be sent back or uploaded.
Author:
Micah Schiewe
